      <title>日本央行鸽派立场推动墨西哥比索引领新兴市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/emerging-markets-sigh-relief-as-dovish-boj-message-weakens-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行暗示将谨慎提高利率之后，墨西哥比索引领新兴市场货币出现反弹，缓解了因投资者放弃日元投资高风险资产而遭受重创的货币压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/emerging-markets-sigh-relief-as-dovish-boj-message-weakens-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行鸽派信号削弱进一步加息预期 日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会进一步提高基准利率，随后日元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
